about.summary: Function to read and write the 'Stata' file format.

name: r-readstata13
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '0.9.2' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-readstata13
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/readstata13_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/readstata13/readstata13_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 8db78caa6fa26de34027a97cc77df4b31fc21cdda1d91dbbc477d863ffe5b80a

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 1002
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}        # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}      # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_cxx') }}        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}make
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-rcpp >=0.11.5
  run:
    - r-base
    - {{ native }}gcc-libs         # [win]
    - r-rcpp >=0.11.5

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('readstata13')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('readstata13')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/sjewo/readstata13
  license: GPL-2
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2'
  summary: Function to read and write the 'Stata' file format.
  license_family: GPL2

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
